title: SUMMER DAZE
description:
SUMMER DAZE 2016

An homage to summer in New York City. It’s east coast in every way. A local group of twenty somethings revel in the sunshine of summer’s final days. They’re cool, confident and they always know the perfect spots. Everyone wants to know where they are and what they’re thinking, listening to, and wearing. A summer of high shine, seasonless suede, sky high platforms, endless ankle straps, refined sneakers – everything always denim friendly. From the boardwalk to the beach, they’re at home in the city’s perfect balance of gritty glow.

They are unapologetic. Effortless. They are Steve Madden personified.

#SM4DAZE
